              <th>Department</th>
              <th>Date</th>
              <th>Start Time</th>
              <th>End Time</th>
              <th>Year Level</th>
              <th>Semester</th>
              <th>Subject Code</th>
              <th>Subject Name</th>
              <th>Observer</th>
              <th>Modality</th>
